0sandwich%20at%20Palace%20Diner%20in%20Biddeford%2C%20Maine%2C%20and%20understood%20why%20it's%20known%20to%20sell%20out%20early.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sandwich's%20crispy%20chicken%20breast%20practically%20dwarfed%20the%20sesame-seed%20bun.%20It%20was%20piled%20high%20with%20coleslaw%20and%20sliced%20jalape%C3%B1os.%20A%20pepperoncini%20pepper%20had%20been%20placed%20on%20top%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20sandwich%20was%20secured%20with%20a%20toothpick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sandwich%20came%20with%20a%20wedge%20salad%20on%20the%20side%2C%20which%20surprised%20me%20as%20most%20chicken%20sandwiches%20I%20usually%20eat%20come%20with%20fries.%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20it%2C%20however%2C%20and%20thought%20the%20crisp%20lettuce%20and%20savory%20dressing%20added%20a%20freshness%20to%20the%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20weren't%20there%20to%20try%20the%20wedge%20salad%2C%20though.%20It%20was%20all%20about%20the%20chicken%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20was%20the%20best%20chicken%20sandwich%20I've%20ever%20had.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20palace%20diner%20biddeford%20maine%20fried%20chicken%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ba1ca8955b01c3294da73c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalace%20Diner%20fried%20chicken%20sandwich%20came%20with%20slaw.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20quite%20a%20few%20chicken%20sandwiches%20in%20my%20lifetime%2C%20so%20this%20was%20a%20high%20honor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalace%20Diner's%20fried%20chicken%20sandwich%20was%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20hold%20in%20one%20hand.%20The%20chicken%20was%20super%20crispy%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20with%20kernels%20of%20fried%20goodness%20creating%20a%20shell%20around%20the%20thick%2C%20moist%20chicken%20breast.%20The%20tangy%20sl