20three%20judges%20concluded%20that%20the%20charges%20made%20by%20India%20against%20Rana%20contained%20distinct%20elements%20from%20the%20crimes%20for%20which%20Rana%20was%20acquitted%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20panel%20also%20held%20that%20India%20gave%20sufficient%20competent%20evidence%20to%20support%20the%20magistrate%20judge's%20finding%20of%20probable%20cause%20that%20Rana%20committed%20the%20charged%20crimes.%20The%20three%20panel%20of%20judges%20were%20Milan%20D%20Smith%2C%20Bridget%20S%20Bade%2C%20and%20Sidney%20A%20Fitzwater.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERana%20was%20tried%20in%20a%20US%20district%20court%20on%20charges%20of%20supporting%20the%20terror%20group%20that%20carried%20out%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks.%20A%20jury%20convicted%20him%20of%20giving%20material%20support%20to%20a%20foreign%20terrorist%20organisation%20and%20conspiring%20to%20provide%20material%20support%20to%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20carry%20out%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Denmark.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20jury%2C%20however%2C%20acquitted%20Rana%20of%20conspiring%20to%20provide%20material%20support%20to%20terrorism%20related%20to%20the%20attacks%20in%20India.%20After%20Rana%20served%20seven%20years%20in%20jail%20for%20those%20convictions%20and%20upon%20his%20compassionate%20release%2C%20India%20issued%20a%20request%20for%20his%20extradition%20to%20try%20him%20for%20his%20link%20with%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERana%20has%20argued%20that%20India%20did%20not%20give%20sufficient%20evidence%20to%20show%20probable%20cause%20that%20he%20committed%20the%20charged%20crimes.%20The%20extradition%20court%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20his%20arguments%20and%20certified%20that%20he%20was%20extraditable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJudge%20Milan%20D%20Smith%20said%20the%20Indo-US%20extradition%20treaty's%20plain%20terms%2C%20the%20post-ratification%20understanding%20of%20the%20signatories%2C%20and%20persuasive%20precedent%20all%20support%20the%20government's%20interpretation%20that%20he%20can%20be%20sent%20to%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20parties%20do%20not%20dispute%20that%20the%20crimes%20charged%20in%20India%20have%20elements%20independent%20from%20those%20under%20which%20Rana%20was%20prosecuted%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20treaty%20permits%20Rana's%20extradition%2C%26quot%3B%20Judge%20Smith%20said.%20Rana%20has%20the%20option%20of%20appealing%20against%20this%20ruling.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723899780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fik9apsg_tahawwur-rana-2008-mumbai-terror-attack-ani_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistan-origin-26-11-mumbai-terror-attacks-accused-tahawwur-rana-can-be-sent-to-india-says-us-court-10-points-6358335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistani-origin%20Canadian%20businessman%20Tahawwur%20Hussain%20Rana%2C%20wanted%20in%20India%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20that%20killed%20over%20160%2C%20can%20be%20sent%20to%20India%20under%20the%20Indo-US%20extradition%20treaty%2C%20a%20court%20in%20California%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistan-origin-26-11-mumbai-terror-attacks-accused-tahawwur-rana-can-be-sent-to-india-says-us-court-10-points-6358335%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Controversy%20mars%20Nadeem's%20gala%20dinner%20as%20Govt%20cancels%20invitations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723899212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112591534%2Cimgsize-53580.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fparis-olympics-2024%2Fcontroversy-mars-arshad-nadeems-gala-dinner-as-pakistan-government-cancels-invitations-of-hockey-s