0and%20Andy%20against%20a%20gruesome%20Xenomorph%2Fhuman%20hybrid%2C%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BOffspring%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20fans%20saw%20something%20similar%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BAlien%3A%20Resurrection%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20creature%20in%20the%202024%20movie%20stands%20head%20and%20shoulders%20above%20the%20version%20from%20the%201997%20film%2C%20both%20literally%20and%20metaphorically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20using%20an%20asteroid%20belt%20to%20kill%20the%20monstrous%20creature%2C%20Rain%20and%20Andy%20settle%20into%20their%20stasis%20pods%20as%20the%20ship%20is%20on%20course%20for%20Yvaga%20III.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dysfunctional%20siblings%20are%20the%20only%20surviving%20members%20of%20the%20crew%2C%20but%20at%20least%20they%20get%20a%20positive%20ending.%20There's%20no%20post-credits%20scene%2C%20but%20the%20story%20leaves%20the%20door%20open%20for%20an%20%26quot%3BAlien%3A%20Romulus%26quot%3B%20sequel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc35a6cd-0e40-466c-843f-b99bc7d1144b%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAlien%3A%20Romulus%202%26quot%3B%20could%20take%20place%20on%20the%20new%20planet.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224607%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20man%20in%20a%20gray%20jumpsuit%20standing%20in%20the%20corridor%20of%20a%20spaceship.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf54795da406397bf682ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Jonsson%20as%20Andy%20in%20%26quot%3BAlien%3A%20Romulus.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3E20th%20Century%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20in%20the%20film%2C%20all%20the%20characters%20reference%20how%20Andy%20will%20not%20be%20welcome%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20which%20is%20free%20from%20Weyland-Yutani's%20control.%20The%20people%20on%20Yvaga%20III%20are%20so%20against%20androids%20that%20anyone%20who%20owns%20one%20is%20thrown%20in%20prison%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they%20originally%20planned%20to%20leave%20Andy%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sequel%20could%20quite%20easily%20pick%20up%20on%20Yvaga%20III%20if%20the%20population%20is%20hostile%20to%20Rain%20and%20Andy.%20And%20although%20Rain%20killed%20the%20Offspring%2C%20something%20could've%20easily%20been%20left%20behind%20on%20their%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20whether%20it's%20a%20Xenomorph%20or%20a%20Facehugger%20could%20be%20left%20up%20to%20the%20writers'%20discretion.%20Maybe%20Weyland-Yutani%20will%20recover%20some%20of%20the%20Offspring's%20DNA%20and%20continue%20the%20twisted%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20%C3%81lvarez%20and%20the%20cast%20haven't%20clarified%20whether%20they%20intend%20to%20make%20a%20sequel%2C%20but%20if%20it's%20successful%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20it's%20not%20hard%20to%20imagine%20that%20Disney%20executives%20will%20be%20keen%20for%20a%20sequel.%20(So%20far%2C%20it's%20off%20to%20a%20solid%20start%20and%20is%20headed%20for%20a%20%2440%20million%20opening%20weekend%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2024%2F08%2Fbox-office-alien-romulus-1236042166%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeadline%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20however%2C%20Hulu%20is%20developing%20an%20%26quot%3BAlien%26quot%3B%20TV%20series%20from%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffargo-season-five-ending-meaning-connections-to-previous-seasons-finale-recap-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFargo%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20creator%20Noah%20Hawley.%20Titled%2C%20%26quot%3BAlien%3A%20Earth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20series%20is%20set%2030%20years%20before%20the%20events%20of%20Ridley%20Scott's%20original%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20is%20known%20about%20the%20plot%2C%20but%20it%20includes%20%26quot%3BAndor%26quot%3B%20star%20Alex%20Lawther%20as%20CJ%2C%20a%20soldier%2C%20and%20Sydney%20Chance%20as%20Wendy%2C%20a%20woman%20with%20the%20body%20of%20an%20adult%20and%20the%20consciousn