Insider%20by%20the%20Center%20of%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20show%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBrianTHart%2Fstatus%2F1819123294924148894%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshipbuilding%20progress%20on%20the%20Type%2076%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Yulan-class%2C%20in%20Shanghai's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EChangxing%20Island%20Shipbuilding%20Base.%20The%20images%2C%20dated%20July%204%2C%20capture%20a%20variety%20of%20details%20about%20the%20vessel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20its%20Type%20075%2C%20Yushen-class%20predecessor%2C%20there%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20number%20of%20notable%20differences.%20Perhaps%20most%20apparent%20is%20the%20size.%20The%20Type%20076%20is%20much%20longer%20and%20larger%20than%20the%20Type%20075%2C%20and%20when%20it%20is%20completed%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20largest%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%20in%20the%20world%2C%20easily%20exceeding%20its%20US%20and%20Japanese%20counterparts%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fanalysis%2Fchinas-massive-next-generation-amphibious-assault-ship-takes-shape%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECSIS%20analysis%20of%20the%20new%20vessel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20satellite%20image%20showing%20China's%20new%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%20being%20built%20in%20a%20shipyard.%20There%20is%20a%20text%20overlay%20showing%20the%20length%20of%20the%20trench%20for%20launching%20aircraft.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf9b335da406397bf6a813%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20satellite%20image%20shows%20the%20Type%2076's%20top%20deck.%3Cp%3ECSIS%2FChina%20Power%2FCNES%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20a%20larger%20warship%20include%20a%20potential%20capacity%20for%20more%20aircraft%2C%20more%20space%20to%20host%20a%20variety%20of%20personnel%20aboard%2C%20and%20internal%20storage%20space%20for%20other%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20perhaps%20the%20aspect%20of%20the%20Type%20076%20that%20stands%20out%20most%20is%20that%20it%20appears%20to%20feature%20a%20catapult%20launching%20system%20for%20fixed-wing%20aircraft%2C%20technology%20also%20featured%20on%20China's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-newest-aircraft-carrier-seen-with-aircraft-mock-ups-images-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20CNS%20Fujian%20aircraft%20carrier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20features%20an%20electromagnetic%20aircraft%20launch%20system%20like%20the%20newest%20US%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20the%20Ford-class%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20something%20that%20we've%20seen%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Funaiole%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20with%20the%20China%20Power%20Project%20at%20CSIS%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BNo%20other%20country%20has%20an%20LHA%20that%20has%20a%20catapult%20system%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20landing%20helicopter%20assault%20ship.%20This%20capability%20would%20put%20the%20warship%20somewhere%20in%20between%20a%20traditional%20assault%20ship%20and%20an%20aircraft%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224812%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20fighter%20jet%20launches%20off%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20with%20a%20jet%20fuel%20blur%20behind%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf9de3b4912df3ae1c68db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223036%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F%2FA-18F%20Super%20Hornet%2C%20assigned%20to%20Air%20Test%20and%20Evaluation%20Squadron%20(VX)%2023%2C%20takes%20off%20from%20USS%20Gerald%20R.%20Ford's%20(CVN%2078)%20flight%20deck.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%202nd%20Class%20Ruben%20Reed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20addition%20of%20a%20catapult%20launch%20system%20on%20the%20Type%20076%20suggests%2C%20Funaiole%20added%2C%20that%20China%20is%20confident%20in%20that%20technology%20despite%20just%20introducing%20it%20on%20the%20Fujian.%20But%20it%20remains%20unclear%20what%20types%20of%20combat%20jets%20China%20would%20launch%20off%20the%20Type%20076%20or%20if%20those%20aircraft%20would%20be%20manned%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Fujian%2C%20China%20made%20a%20technological%20leap%20from%20the%20ski-jump-style%20aircraft%20launch%20systems%20of%20its%20earlier%20carriers%20to%20advanced%20electromagnetic%20catapults%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-new-aircraft-carrier-more-to-learn-to-match-us-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompletely%20skipping%20over%20steam-powered%20catapults%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20J-15%20fighter%20taking%20off%20from%20aircraft%20carrier%20Shandong%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658e128cc442a2f676c6fa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20J-15%20fighter%20takes%20off%20from%20aircraft%20carrier%20Shandong%20during%20the%20combat%20readiness%20patrol%20and%20military%20exercises%20around%20Taiwan.%3Cp%3EAn%20Ni%2FXinhua%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20could%20use%20the%20catapult%20system%2C%20as%20experts%20and%20top%20China%20watchers%20have%20suggested%2C%20to%20launch%20unmanned%20aerial%20vehicles.%20But%20if%20it%20can%2C%20despite%20operational%20and%20technological%20constraints%2C%20launch%20manned%20aircraft%2C%20that%20would%20make%20the%20Type%2076%20almost%20a%20hybrid%2C%20mini-carrier%20of%20sorts%2C%20filling%20an%20unusual%20role.%20The%20catapults%2C%20wide%20flight%20deck%2C%20and%20clear%20runway%20would%20support%20that%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Clark%2C%