t%20is%20as%20important%2C%20if%20not%20more%20important%2C%20to%20emphasize%20how%20mind-bogglingly%20impressive%20China's%20ability%20to%20build%20ships%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Funaiole%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20while%20the%20exact%20timeline%20of%20its%20construction%20is%20unclear%2C%20China%20started%20building%20the%20076%2C%20likely%20prioritizing%20it%2C%20while%20finishing%20the%20new%20dry%20dock%20it%20was%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20just%20a%20small%20example%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-us-navy-shipbuilding-projects-are-delayed-by-years-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapacity%20and%20size%20of%20China's%20shipbuilding%20power%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20big%20takeaway%20from%20the%20Type%20076's%20building%2C%20Clark%20said%2C%20is%20it%20shows%20how%20once%20China's%20%26quot%3Bgot%20a%20hot%20production%20line%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bable%20to%20leverage%20commercial%20shipbuilding%20capacity%20essentially%20for%20military%20ship%20construction%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20%26quot%3Bcan%20build%20ships%2C%20like%20a%20Type%20076%2C%20pretty%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20satellite%20image%20shows%20China's%20new%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%20being%20built%20alongside%20other%20vessels.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf9b751aa2ac29ee31f705%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20satellite%20image%20showing%20the%20Type%2076%20being%20built%20around%20other%20vessels.%3Cp%3ECSIS%2FChina%20Power%2FCNES%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20how%20unusual%20the%20Type%2076%20appears%20to%20be%2C%20the%20US%20certainly%20could've%20accomplished%20a%20vessel%20of%20this%20nature%2C%20Funaiole%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20US%20has%20%26quot%3Bleaned%20quite%20heavily%20and%20rightfully%20so%20on%20supercarriers%2C%26quot%3B%20Fu