ch.%20One%20night%2C%20we%20were%20sitting%20on%20the%20couch%20when%20my%20husband%20picked%20the%20book%20up.%20He%20dragged%20his%20thumb%20across%20the%20side%20of%20the%20book%2C%20stopped%20on%20a%20random%20page%2C%20then%20opened%20the%20book%20and%20looked%20down.%20It%20had%20landed%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BH%26quot%3B%20section.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20name%20he%20read%20on%20the%20top%20left%20was%20%26quot%3BHarley.%26quot%3B%20Harley%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-has-gender-neutral-name-has-mixed-feelings-about-it-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egender-neutral%20name%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(we%20kept%20the%20baby's%20sex%20a%20surprise)%20of%20British%20origin.%20It's%20derived%20from%20the%20Old%20English%20words%20hara%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bhare%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20leah%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bmeadow.%26quot%3B%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20recently%20moved%20back%20to%20Australia%20from%20London%2C%20and%20I%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20our%20child%20a%20name%20with%20a%20UK%20connection.%20I%20also%20liked%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20couldn't%20really%20shorten%20it%20to%20a%20nickname.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHarley%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20repeated%20back.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20our%20son%20was%20born%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%20I%20took%20one%20look%20at%20him%20and%20knew%20the%20name%20fit.%20We%20called%20him%20Harley%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-maiden-name-middle-names-family-legacy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egave%20him%20the%20middle%20name%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Samuel%2C%20after%20my%20husband.%20He's%20the%20only%20Harley%20at%20his%20school%2C%20and%20the%20name%20suits%20him%20to%20a%20tee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20da