c-national-convention-preview-harris-gaza-war-protests-election-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pawar%20slams%20PM's%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20stance%20amid%20delayed%20Maha%20poll%20dates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723893132000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112589584%2Cimgsize-628729.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-truth-in-pawar-slams-pm-modis-one-nation-one-election-stance-amid-delayed-maharashtra-poll-dates%2Farticleshow%2F112589413.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar%20criticized%20PM%20Modi%20for%20advocating%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20during%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20but%20not%20scheduling%20elections%20for%20Maharashtra.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20has%20announced%20polls%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Haryana%20but%20cited%20security%20concerns%20for%20delaying%20Maharashtra's%20election%20dates.%20CEC%20hinted%20Maharashtra%20elections%20might%20happen%20after%20Diwali%20due%20to%20logistical%20and%20festive%20considerations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-truth-in-pawar-slams-pm-modis-one-nation-one-election-stance-amid-delayed-maharashtra-poll-dates%2Farticleshow%2F112589413.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Can%20India%20Create%20More%20Jobs%3F%20IMF's%20Gita%20Gopinath%20Has%20Some%20Tips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20need%20a%20multi-pronged%20approach%20to%20create%20jobs%20instead%20of%20targeting%20only%20a%20few%20areas%20to%20add%20more%20workers%2C%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20First%20Deputy%20Managing%20Director%20Gita%20Gopinath%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20at%20least%20in%20India%2C%20any%20disruption%20caused%20by%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20in%20the%20jobs%20sector%20will%20have%20a%20lower%20impact%20as%20a%20majority%20of%20India's%20workforce%20is%20in%20labour-intensive%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20done%20extremely%20well%20in%20headline%20growth%20numbers...%20It%20is%20the%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20growth%20has%20averaged%20around%206.6%20per%20cent.%20Certainly%20India's%20growth%20has%20been%20much%20more%20capital%20intensive%2C%20but%20much%20less%20in%20hiring%20a%20lot%20more%20workers%2C%20in%20creating%20a%20lot%20more%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gopinath%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20gave%20a%20small%20list%20of%20to-dos%20in%20order%20to%20create%20more%20jobs%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20near-term%2C%20it%20is%20helpful%20to%20improve%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%20We%20see%20that%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Removing%20trade%20restrictions%20also%20plays%20a%20very%20important%20role.%20Public%20infrastructure%20investment%20is%20already%20happening%2C%20and%20more%20of%20that%20will%20absolutely%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20key%20IMF%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20to%20make%20this%20a%20medium-long%20term%20growth%20story%20requires%20more%20investment%20in%20human%20capital%20and%20scaling%20up%20the%20workforce.%20You%20look%20at%20India's%20workforce%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20years%20of%20education.%20It%20is%20much%20lower%20compared%20to%20its%20peers.%20So%20investing%20in%20raising%20the%20skill%20level%20of%20the%20country%20is%20going%20to%20be%20absolutely%20critical%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gopinath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20creating%20jobs%20has%20to%20be%20a%20multi-pronged%20approach.%20%26quot%3BThe%20numbers%20are%20large.%20It%20cannot%20be%20done%20by%20targeting%20a%20few%20areas.%20It's%20going%20to%20require%20broad-based%20job%20creation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20concerns%20over%20AI%20derailing%20India's%20plans%20and%20policies%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20jobs%2C%20the%20Indian-origin%20IMF%20officer%20said%20only%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20workforce%20is%20at%20risk%20of%20displacement%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20a%20majority%20of%20India's%20workforce%20is%20in%20labour-intensive%20agriculture%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20be%20lower.%20We%20assume%2024%20per%20cent%20(of%20India's%20workforce)%20is%20exposed%20to%20AI%2C%20of%20which%2010%20per%20cent%20is%20at%20risk%20of%20displacement.%20This%20is%20a%20small%20number.%20The%20question%20is%20what%20are%20we%20going%20to%20see%20around%20the%20world%3F%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gopinath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20IMF%2C%20Mr%20Gopinath%20oversees%20the%20work%20of%20staff%2C%20represents%20the%20fund%20at%20multilateral%20forums%2C%20maintains%20high-level%20contacts%20with%20member%20governments%20and%20board%20members%2C%20the%20media%2C%20and%20other%20institutions%2C%20and%20leads%20the%20IMF's%20work%20on%20surveillance%20and%20related%20policies%2C%20and%20oversees%20research%20and%20flagship%20publications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20Chief%20Economist%20of%20the%20IMF%20from%202019-22.%20In%20that%20role%2C%20she%20was%20the%20Economic%20Counsellor%20of%20the%20IMF%20and%20Director%20of%20its%20Research%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723893120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fbm9hb028_gita-gopinath_625x300_17_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-can-india-create-more-jobs-imfs-gita-gopinath-has-some-tips-6357893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20need%20a%20multi-pronged%20approach%20to%20create%20jobs%20instead%20of%20targeting%20only%20a%20few%20areas%20to%20add%20more%20workers%2C%20the%20Intern