ocratically%20elected%20government%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20JD(S)%2C%20and%20others%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gehlot%20has%20sanctioned%20his%20prosecution%20in%20the%20MUDA%20land%20scam%20case%20after%20petitions%20by%20three%20activists%20-%20Pradeep%20Kumar%2C%20TJ%20Abraham%2C%20and%20Snehamayi%20Krishna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complaint%20filed%20with%20the%20Lokayukta%20police%20in%20July%2C%20Mr%20Abraham%20alleged%20that%20the%20allotment%20of%2014%20alternative%20sites%20in%20an%20upscale%20Mysuru%20neighbourhood%20to%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20BM%20Parvathi%20was%20illegal%2C%20which%20caused%20the%20exchequer%20a%20Rs%2045%20crore%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20named%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20son%20S%20Yathindra%2C%20and%20senior%20MUDA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20activist%2C%20Snehamayi%20Krishna%20also%20alleged%20the%20involvement%20of%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20and%20MUDA%20and%20administrative%20officials%20in%20the%20alleged%20land%20scam.%20A%20fresh%20FIR%20was%20not%20filed%20as%20the%20police%20said%20a%20probe%20was%20already%20underway%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddaramaiah%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20land%20for%20which%20his%20wife%20received%20compensation%2C%20was%20gifted%20by%20her%20brother%20Mallikarjuna%20in%201998.%20But%20activist%20Krishna%20alleged%20that%20Mallikarjuna%20had%20procured%20it%20illegally%20in%202004%20and%20got%20it%20registered%20using%20forged%20documents%20with%20the%20help%20of%20government%20and%20revenue%20officials.%20The%20land%20was%20shown%20to%20have%20been%20bought%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Parvathi%20sought%20compensation%20for%20this%20land%20in%202014%20when%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BConspiracy%26quot%3B%3A%20DK%20Shivakumar%20Backs%20Siddaramaiah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20on%20Saturday%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20state%20government%20will%20put%20all%20their%20weight%20behind%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20fight%20it%20legally%20and%20we%20will%20fight%20it%20politically%20as%20well...%20This%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20clear%20conspiracy%20against%20backward-class%20Siddaramaiah%20who%20is%20running%20the%20government%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20are%20trying%20to%20destabilise%20the%20government%20by%20using%20the%20Governor's%20office.%20This%20is%20unfortunate...%20There%20is%20no%20question%20of%20him%20resigning.%20He%20will%20continue%20in%20the%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Karnataka%20Minister%20Krishna%20Byregowda%20also%20said%20the%20procedure%20adopted%20by%20the%20Governor%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20illegal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723886280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fu0qquu9o_siddaramaiah-karnataka-governor_625x300_17_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-on-thaawarchand-gehlots-prosecution-sanction-in-muda-scam-case-anti-constitution-against-law-6357095%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Governor%20Thaawarchand%20Gehlot%20has%20granted%20sanction%20for%20the%20prosecution%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20MUDA%20site%20allotment%20'scam'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-on-thaawarchand-gehlots-prosecution-sanction-in-muda-scam-case-anti-constitution-against-law-6357095%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20to%20form%20committee%20for%20medical%20staff%20safety%20amid%20Kolkata%20tragedy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723884931000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112586507%2Cimgsize-1351273.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcentre-to-form-committee-to-ensure-medical-staffs-safety-amid-uproar-over-kolkata-tragedy%2Farticleshow%2F112586289.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20formed%20a%20committee%20to%20enhance%20healthcare%20professionals'%20safety%20after%20concerns%20from%20various%20stakeholders.%20State%20governments%20were%20invited%20for%20suggestions%2C%20and%20healthcare%20workers%20were%20asked%20to%20resume%20duties%20amidst%20rising%20Dengue%20and%20Malaria%20cases.%20The%20government%20mandated%20FIRs%20within%20six%20hours%20for%20any%20violence%20against%20medical%20staff%20following%20a%20rape-murder%20incident%20in%20Kolkata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcentre-to-form-committee-to-ensure-medical-staffs-safety-amid-uproar-over-kolkata-tragedy%2Farticleshow%2F112586289.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre's%20Appeal%20To%20Doctors%20Amid%20Nationwide%20Protests%20Over%20Kolkata%20Horror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-case-live-news-updates-doctors-begin-24-hour-strike-over-rg-kar-medical-college-and-hospital-incident-6355362%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enationwide%20strike%20by%20doctors%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20the%20Union%20Health%20Ministry%20today%20assured%20them%20of%20all%20possible%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20said%20it%20will%20form%20a%20committee%20to%20suggest%20measures%20for%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20healthcare%20professionals%2C%20an%20announcement%20that%20came%20over%20a%20week%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fkolkata-rg-kar-hospital-doctor-rape-murder-fractures-150-mg-semen-other-claims-denied-by-cops-in-kolkata-rape-murder-6356105%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20triggered%20widespread%20protests%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assurances%20came%20after%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20Federation%20of%20Resident%20Doctors%20Association%20(FORDA)%2C%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%2C%20and%20Resident%20Doctors'%20Associations%20of%20Governmental%20Medical%20Colleges%20%26amp%3B%20Hospitals%20of%20Delhi%20met%20the%20officials%20of%20the%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20associations%20have%20put%20forth%20their%20demands%20regarding%20their%20concern%20over%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20healthcare%20workers%20at%20the%20workplace.%20The%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Welfare%20has%20heard%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20representatives%20and%20assured%20them%20of%20all%20possible%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20the%20security%20of%20healthcare%20professionals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20representatives%20of%20all%20the%20associations%20were%20informed%20that%20the%20Government%20is%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20is%20sensitive%20to%20their%20demands.%20It%20was%20observed%20that%2026%20states%20have%20already%20passed%20legislation%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20healthcare%20workers%20in%20their%20respective%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20of%20all%20stakeholders%20including%20the%20State%20Governments%20will%20be%20invited%20to%20share%20their%20suggestions%20with%20the%20Committee%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20also%20requested%20the%20agitating%20doctors%20to%20resume%20their%20duties%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Blarger%20public%20interest%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20view%20of%20the%20rising%20cases%20of%20dengue%20and%20malaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E5%20Demands%20Of%20Doctors%20On%20Nationwide%20Strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20put%20forth%20the%20following%20five%20demands%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20wants%20a%20significant%20policy%20to%20address%20violence%20against%20doctors%20and%20hospitals.%20The%20doctors'%20body%20is%20pushing%20for%20a%20Central%20Act%20that%20would%20incorporate%20the%20amendments%20made%20in%202023%20to%20the%20Epidemic%20Diseases%20Act%20of%201897%20into%20the%20proposed%20Hospital%20Protection%20Bill%20of%202019.%20This%20move%2C%20it%20said%2C%20would%20strengthen%20the%20existing%20legislation%20in%2025%20states.%20The%20IMA%20has%20suggested%20that%20an%20ordinance%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20enacted%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20would%20be%20appropriate%20in%20this%20situation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20also%20demanded%20that%20hospitals%20be%20declared%20safe%20zones%20with%20the%20first%20step%20being%20mandatory%20security%20entitlements.%20%26quot%3BThe%20security%20protocols%20of%20all%20hospitals%20should%20be%20no%20less%20than%20(that%20of)%20an%20airport.%20Declaring%20the%20hospitals%20as%20safe%20zones%20with%20mandatory%20security%20entitlements%20is%20the%20first%20step.%20CCTVs%2C%20deployment%20of%20security%20personnel%2C%20and%20the%20protocols%20can%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20demanded%20a%20thorough%20overhaul%20of%20the%20working%20and%20living%20conditions%20of%20resident%20doctors%2C%20including%20the%2036-hour%20duty%20shift%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20in%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20safe%20spaces%20to%20take%20a%20rest.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IMA%20has%20also%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmeticulous%20and%20professional%26quot%3B%20investigation%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20horror%20in%20a%20specific%20time%20frame%20and%20rendering%20of%20justice%20besides%20identifying%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20vandalism%20of%20the%20hospital%20premises%20and%20awarding%20exemplary%20punishment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20doctors'%20body%20has%20also%20sought%20an%20appropriate%20and%20dignified%20compensation%20to%20the%20bereaved%20family%20commensurate%20with%20the%20cruelty%20inflicted.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723884420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fk2d8bgqg_doctors-strike_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-set-up-committee-for-safety-of-doctors-amid-nationwide-protests-6356885%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20have%20called%20a%2024-hour%20nationwide%20strike%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20junior%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-set-up-committee-for-safety-of-doctors-amid-nationwide-protests-6356885%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thank%20you%20for%20...'%3A%20What%20Kamala%20Harris%20said%20about%20Meghan%20Markle%20as%20rumors%20swirl%20of%20Duchess'%20possible%202024%20endorsement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723884244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112586269%2Cimgsize-113312.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-elections-kamala-harris-said-about-meghan-markle-as-rumors-swirl-of-duchess-possible-2024-endorsement%2Farticleshow%2F112586040.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%