ed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20just%20no%20words%20to%20describe%20how%20great%20a%20guy%20Mike%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20super%20good%20man%2C%20good%20to%20his%20customers%2C%20loved%20his%20family%20and%20would%20have%20helped%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patricia%20Howard%2C%20another%20regular%20customer%20at%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723883700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm3lfsu7o_gun-violence-reuters_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fus-teen-robs-convenience-store-then-kills-man-of-indian-origin-6356943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2036-year-old%20Indian-origin%20man%20has%20been%20shot%20and%20killed%20after%20a%20teenage%20boy%20robbed%20a%20convenience%20store%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20North%20Carolina%2C%20authorities%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fus-teen-robs-convenience-store-then-kills-man-of-indian-origin-6356943%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shahrukh%20Khan%20on%20dream%20of%20being%20an%20action%20hero%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723883618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112586143%2Cimgsize-24672.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshahrukh-khan-opens-up-about-his-dream-of-being-an-action-hero-i-wanted-a-six-pack-and-a-lady-by-my-side%2Farticleshow%2F112586167.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112586167.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20embraced%20a%20new%20challenge%20in%20the%20action%20film%20Jawan%2C%20fulfilling%20a%20lifelong%20dream%20of%20portraying%20an%20action%20hero%20with%20six-pack%20abs.%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20he%20stayed%20fit%20by%20working%20out%20regularly%20and%20eating%20one%20meal%20a%20day.%20Khan's%20upcoming%20project%2C%20King%2C%20features%20his%20daughter%20Suhana%20Khan%20and%20Abhishek%20Bachchan%2C%20and%20explores%20intense%20survival%20challenges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshahrukh-khan-opens-up-about-his-dream-of-being-an-action-hero-i-wanted-a-six-pack-and-a-lady-by-my-side%2Farticleshow%2F112586167.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Poison%20Tablets%20To%20Cigars%3A%20How%20CIA%20Tried%20To%20Assassinate%20Fidel%20Castro%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Cuban%20President%20Fidel%20Castro%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2090%20from%20natural%20causes.%20However%2C%20not%20many%20know%20that%20the%20revolutionary%20leader%20survived%20not%2010%20or%2020%20but%20over%20600%20assassination%20attempts.%20For%20almost%20half%20a%20century%2C%20the%20attempts%20at%20Cuba's%20most%20iconic%20leader%20involved%20spies%2C%20Mafia%20hitmen%2C%20James%20Bond-style%20death%20devices%2C%20and%20other%20methods%20that%20may%20seem%20like%20something%20out%20of%20an%20Ian%20Fleming%20novel.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%2C%20a%20new%20docuseries%2C%20Mafia%20Spies%2C%20streaming%20on%20Paramount%2B%2C%20exposed%20the%20actual%20how%20the%20CIA%20cooperated%20with%20the%20mafia%20to%20organise%20Castro's%20assassination.%20It's%20based%20on%20a%20book%2C%20authored%20by%20Thomas%20Maier%2C%20of%20the%20same%20name.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20intricate%20storylines%20and%20large%20ensemble%20of%20politicians%2C%20mobsters%2C%20spies%2C%20revolutionaries%2C%20and%20entertainers%20feature%20in%20the%20six%20episodes%20of%20Mafia%20Spies.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCastro%20was%20the%20newly%20appointed%20prime%20minister%20of%20Cuba%2C%20and%20the%20CIA%2C%20then%20headed%20by%20Allen%20Dulles%2C%20intended%20to%20topple%20him.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20assassinate%20Castro%2C%20the%20CIA%20recruited%20organised%20criminal%20figures%2C%20Sam%20Giancana%20and%20John%20Roselli%20of%20the%20Chicago%20Outfit%2C%20through%20a%20middleman%20named%20Robert%20Maheu%2C%20who%20was%20an%20attorney%20and%20businessman.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNotably%2C%20the%20mafia%20had%20their%20own%20motivations%20for%20wanting%20Castro%20gone%20as%20Havana's%20casinos%20ceased%20to%20be%20a%20cash%20cow%20sanctuary%20for%20them%20when%20he%20took%20over%20in%201959.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20series%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20unsuccessful%201961%20Bay%20of%20Pigs%20invasion%20of%20Cuba%2C%20the%201962%20Cuban%20Missile%20Crisis%20and%20the%201963%20assassination%20of%20US%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20accomplish%20its%20aim%2C%20the%20CIA%20and%20its%20mafia%20allies%20used%20everything%20from%20poison%20tablets%20to%20a%20deadly%20%26quot%3Bhoney%20pot%26quot%3B%20that%20involved%20enlisting%20a%20woman%20to%20murder%20and%20seduce.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMaier's%20book%20is%20based%20in%20large%20part%20on%20documents%20on%20Kennedy's%20assassination%20that%20the%20National%20Archives%20published%20in%20batches%20in%202017%20and%202018.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20JFK%20records%20demonstrate%20that%20despite%20their%20deadly%20reputation%2C%20Giancana%20and%20Roselli%2C%20the%20Mafia%20duo%2C%20were%20unable%20to%20assassinate%20Castro.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20potential%20assassin%20in%20Havana%20was%20handed%20poison%20tablets%20by%20the%20CIA.%20However%2C%20he%20got%20cold%20feet%20before%20tampering%20with%20Castro's%20food.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Church%20Committee%2C%20a%20Senate%20committee%20that%20documented%20abuses%20by%20intelligence%20services%20in%20the%20mid-1970s%2C%20claims%20that%20the%20cigar%20plot%2C%20perhaps%20the%20most%20well-known%20attempt%20on%20Castro's%20life%2C%20began%20in%201960.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20Committee's%20investigation%2C%20an%20official%20was%20handed%20a%20box%20of%20Castro's%20favourite%20cigars%20along%20with%20orders%20to%20inject%20them%20with%20deadly%20poison.%20The%20cigars%20were%20tainted%20with%20a%20botulinum%20toxin%20so%20strong%20that%20ingesting%20one%20would%20result%20in%20death.%20It%20is%20unclear%20from%20the%20record%20if%20there%20was%20an%20effort%20to%20give%20Castro%20the%20cigars.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCastro%20loved%20scuba%20diving%2C%20so%20it%20should%20come%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20CIA%20investigated%20the%20potential%20of%20creating%20an%20explosive%20seashell%20to%20assassinate%20him%20during%20one%20of%20his%20outings.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20Church%20Committee%20report%2C%20in%201963%2C%20Desmond%20Fitzgerald%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20%5Banti-Castro%20CIA%5D%20Task%20Force%2C%20ordered%20his%20assistant%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20it%20would%20be%20possible%20to%20place%20a%20seashell%20that%20could%20be%20set%20to%20detonate%20in%20a%20place%20where%20Castro%20frequently%20went%20diving.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOther%20unsuccessful%20Florida-based%20commando%20operations%20were%20attributed%20to%20misfortune%20or%20inauspicious%20timing.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFighters%20with%20CIA%20training%20who%20were%20discovered%20invading%20Cuban%20coastlines%20during%20nighttime%20assaults%20were%20frequently%20imprisoned%20and%20occasionally%20put%20to%20death%20by%20firing%20squad.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20JFK%20documents%20also%20show%20how%20Castro's%20own%20network%20of%20double%20agents%20and%20supporters%20in%20Florida%20thwarted%20CIA%20operations%20and%20assisted%20in%20protecting%20the%20communist%20leader.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20few%20of%20the%20conspirators%20who%20were%20associated%20with%20the%20two%20gangsters%20betrayed%20them%20for%20personal%20gain.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723882020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-12%2Ffidel-castro_650x400_71480827717.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrom-poison-tablets-to-cigars-how-the-us-tried-and-failed-to-kill-fidel-castro-6356579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20JFK%20documents%20also%20show%20how%20Castro's%20own%20network%20of%20double%20agents%20and%20supporters%20in%20Florida%20thwarted%20CIA%20operations%20and%20assisted%20in%20protecting%20the%20communist%20leader.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrom-poison-tablets-to-cigars-how-the-us-tried-and-failed-to-kill-fidel-castro-6356579%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-Origin%20man%20shot%20dead%20by%20teenager%20in%20convenience%20store%20robbery%20in%20North%20Carolina%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723881799000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112585541%2Cimgsize-6534.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-origin-man-shot-dead-by-teenager-in-convenience-store-robbery-in-north-carolina%2Farticleshow%2F112583891.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112583891.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-origin-man-shot-dead-by-teenager-in-co