0in%20Africa%20since%20January%3A%20Health%20agency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723880753000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112585253%2Cimgsize-721219.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmore-than-18700-mpox-cases-detected-in-africa-since-january-health-agency%2Farticleshow%2F112585161.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112585161.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20African%20Union%20health%20agency%20reported%2018%2C737%20suspected%20or%20confirmed%20mpox%20cases%20in%20Africa%20this%20year%2C%20including%201%2C200%20in%20one%20week.%20The%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%2C%20hardest%20hit%2C%20saw%201%2C005%20cases%20and%2024%20deaths%20recently.%20Across%2012%20African%20Union%20states%2C%203%2C101%20confirmed%20and%2015%2C636%20suspected%20cases%20were%20reported%2C%20resulting%20in%20541%20deaths.%20WHO%20declared%20an%20international%20health%20emergency%20for%20the%20new%20Clade%201b%20strain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmore-than-18700-mpox-cases-detected-in-africa-since-january-health-agency%2Farticleshow%2F112585161.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmore-than-18700-mpox-cases-detected-in-africa-since-january-health-agency%2Famp_articleshow%2F112585161.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmore-than-18700-mpox-cases-detected-in-africa-since-january-health-agency%2Famp_articleshow%2F112585161.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Is%20MUDA%20Row%20In%20Which%20Siddaramaiah%20Will%20Be%20Prosecuted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20faces%20a%20big%20challenge%20as%20the%20Governor%20has%20sanctioned%20his%20prosecution%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20site%20allotment%20by%20the%20Mysuru%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20(MUDA).%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20campaigning%20against%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20his%20government%20over%20the%20alleged%20land%20scam%20and%20demanding%20his%20resignation.%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20denied%20all%20charges%20against%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20BM%20Parvathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20The%20Row%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MUDA%20land%20scam%20row%20pertains%20to%20the%20allotment%20of%20compensatory%20land%20parcels%20to%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20when%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Social%20activists%20allege%20irregularities%20in%20the%20process%20that%20allegedly%20caused%20loss%20worth%20crores%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer.%20Top%20officials%20in%20the%20MUDA%20and%20revenue%20department%20are%20also%20named%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20three%20activists%20-Pradeep%20Kumar%2C%20TJ%20Abraham%2C%20and%20Snehamayi%20Krishna%20-%20had%20requested%20Governor%20Thaawarchand%20Gehlot%20for%20action%20against%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abraham%2C%20an%20anti-corruption%20activist%2C%20had%20alleged%20the%20multi-crore%20scam%20caused%20huge%20losses%20to%20the%20state%20exchequer%20in%20his%20petition%20to%20the%20Governor%20and%20requested%20him%20to%20sanction%20his%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-chief-minister-siddaramaiah-to-be-prosecuted-in-land-scam-case-6355735%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20To%20Be%20Prosecuted%20In%20Land%20Scam%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20he%20had%20complained%20to%20the%20Lokayukta%20police%20that%20the%20allotment%20of%2014%20sites%20in%20an%20upscale%20Mysuru%20neighbourhood%20to%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20BM%20Parvathi%20was%20illegal.%20This%20caused%20a%20Rs%2045%20crore%20loss%2C%20he%20had%20claimed.%20Besides%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20the%20complaint%20also%20named%20his%20wife%2C%20son%20S%20Yathindra%2C%20and%20senior%20MUDA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20activist%2C%20Snehamayi%20Krishna%20also%20alleged%20the%20involvement%20of%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20and%20MUDA%20and%20administrative%20officials%20in%20the%20alleged%20land%20scam.%20A%20fresh%20FIR%20was%20not%20filed%20as%20the%20police%20said%20probe%20was%20already%20underway%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESiddaramaiah's%20Defence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramiah%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20land%20for%20which%20his%20wife%20received%20compensation%2C%20was%20gifted%20by%20her%20brother%20Mallikarjuna%20in%201998.%20But%20activist%20Krishna%20alleged%20that%20Mallikarjuna%20had%20procured%20it%20illegally%20in%202004%20and%20got%20it%20registered%20it%20using%20forged%20documents%20with%20the%20help%20of%20government%20and%20revenue%20officials.%20The%20land%20was%20shown%20to%20have%20been%20bought%20in%201998.%20Ms%20Parvathi%20sought%20compensation%20for%20this%20land%20in%202014%2C%20when%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20had%20denied%20the%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20motivated%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20his%20wife%20was%20awarded%20compensation%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%20and%20that%20it%20was%20her%20right.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20gave%20the%20site%2C%20now%20if%20they%20call%20it%20illegal%2C%20how%20should%20one%20respond%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAction%20In%20MUDA%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Thaawarchand%20Gehlot%20has%20sanctioned%20the%20Lokayukta%20to%20prosecute%20Siddar