ing-in-milwaukee-what-happened%2Farticleshow%2F112583907.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-elections-campaign-plane-carrying-jd-vance-forced-to-make-emergency-landing-in-milwaukee-what-happened%2Famp_articleshow%2F112583907.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-elections-campaign-plane-carrying-jd-vance-forced-to-make-emergency-landing-in-milwaukee-what-happened%2Famp_articleshow%2F112583907.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20Helped%20Create%20A%20Monster%20-%20The%20Era%20Of%20Trumpism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20help%20but%20feel%20sorry%20for%20Rupert%20Murdoch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mary%20Shelley's%20famous%20novel%2C%20Dr%20Frankenstein%20created%20a%20monster%20that%20took%20on%20a%20life%20of%20its%20own%2C%20and%20which%20he%20could%20no%20longer%20control.%20Murdoch%20has%20outdone%20Frankenstein%20and%20created%20two%20monsters%20over%20which%20he%20has%20now%20lost%20control.%20They%20have%20left%20him%20floundering%20and%20threaten%20to%20inflict%20great%20damage%20on%20US%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupert%20Murdoch's%20first%20monster%20is%20the%20Fox%20News%20audience%2C%20which%20after%20long%20cultivation%20into%20the%20Fox%20News%20fantasy%20land%2C%20refuses%20to%20believe%20any%20news%20that%20does%20not%20fit%20its%20prejudices.%20Fox%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20feels%20compelled%20to%20reinforce%20its%20delusions%20rather%20than%20report%20accurately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurdoch's%20second%20monster%20grew%20out%20of%20the%20first%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Donald%20Trump-dominated%20Republican%20Party.%20Murdoch%20wanted%20to%20make%20Trump%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F2%2F28%2F23617987%2Ffox-news-rupert-murdoch-dominion-trump-election-fraud%5C%22%3Enon-person%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%20Milwaukee%20last%20month%20showed%20Trump%20now%20dominates%20the%20party%20like%20no%20one%20else%20in%20living%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%E2%80%98Red%20meat'%20to%20conservatives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Fox%20News%20began%20in%201996%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20for%20its%20first%2020%20years%2C%20Roger%20Ailes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDark-Genius-Influential-Legendary-Political%2Fdp%2F1402754450%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupert%20Murdoch%20and%20I%20and%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20American%20people%20believe%20that%20most%20of%20the%20news%20tilts%20to%20the%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Fox%20News%20was%20never%20just%20a%20mainstream%20news%20service%20with%20a%20somewhat%20more%20conservative%20centre%20of%20gravity.%20From%20the%20beginning%2C%20it%20was%20more%20of%20a%20propaganda%20machine%2C%20and%20this%20became%20increasingly%20pronounced%20over%20the%20years.%20More%20and%20more%2C%20its%20prime-time%20offerings%20consisted%20of%20commentary%20rather%20than%20news%20programs%2C%20designed%20to%20feed%20%E2%80%9Cred%20meat%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20Republican%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20that%20didn't%20fit%20increasingly%20didn't%20appear.%20So%2C%20when%20the%20Iraq%20war%20began%2C%20there%20was%20noisy%20flag-waving%2C%20but%20as%20it%20became%20militarily%20messier%2C%20the%20network%20gave%20it%20much%20less%20attention%2C%20although%20there%20were%20always%20efforts%20to%20find%20a%20positive%20gloss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Barack%20Obama's%20first%20presidential%20term%2C%20Fox%20News%20acted%20as%20a%20recruiting%20and%20publicity%20vehicle%20for%20the%20far-right%2C%20populist%20Tea%20Party.%20It%20gave%20oxygen%20to%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FPolitics%2Fdonald-trump-perpetuated-birther-movement-years%2Fstory%3Fid%3D42138176%5C%22%3Ebaseless%20claim%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Obama%20was%20not%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20therefore%20was%20not%20eligible%20to%20be%20president.%20Fox%20News%20host%20Glenn%20Beck%20asserted%20Obama%20was%20a%20racist%20with%20a%20deep-seated%20hatred%20for%20white%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20it%20often%20denied%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20and%20gave%20publicity%20to%20anti-vaxxer%20views%20and%20quack%20cures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20after%20Trump's%20election%20defeat%20in%202020%2C%20many%20Fox%20News%20viewers%20were%20ready%20to%20believe%20his%20claims%20of%20electoral%20fraud.%20Overwhelmingly%2C%20however%2C%20the%20key%20players%20at%20Fox%20News%20and%20in%20the%20Murdoch%20stable%20believed%20the%20election%20was%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFox%20News's%20chief%20political%20correspondent%20Bret%20Baier%20saw%20%E2%80%9Cno%20evidence%20of%20fraud.%20None.%E2%80%9D%20Murdoch's%20New%20York%20Post%20urged%20Trump%20to%20accept%20the%20result.%20In%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2020%2F11%2F07%2Fpresident-trump-your-legacy-is-secure-stop-the-stolen-election-rhetoric%2F%5C%22%3Eeditorial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20tabloid%20said%20his%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20stolen%20election%20rhetoric%20%E2%80%9Cundermines%20faith%20in%20democracy%20and%20faith%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20new%20threat%20and%20new%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVery%20soon%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20crisis%20overcame%20Fox%20News.%20Its%20prime-time%20ratings%20had%20fallen%2C%20and%20by%20some%20measures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Ftommybeer%2F2021%2F01%2F16%2Ffox-news-viewership-plummets-first-time-behind-cnn-and-msnbc-in-two-decades%2F%5C%22%3ECNN%20was%20now%20ahead%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20most%20spooked%20the%20network's%20management%2C%20however%2C%20was%20that%20two%20small%20news%20operations%2C%20Newsmax%20and%20One%20America%20News%20Network%20(OAN)%2C%20which%20were%20even%20more%20right-wing%20than%20Fox%2C%20were%20being%20publicly%20praised%20by%20Trump%20and%20had%20picked%20up%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFox's%20sense%20of%20crisis%20led%20it%20on%20a%20fateful%20path.%20It%20may%20have%20been%20a%20panicky%20overreaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20post-election%20decline%20in%20viewership%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20among%20those%20of%20the%20losing%20party%20%E2%80%93%20is%20not%20unusual.%20After%20Obama's%20victory%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Fox%20quickly%20regained%20ground%2C%20becoming%20the%20strongest%20opposition%20voice%20against%20the%20new%20administration.%20Moreover%2C%20even%20though%20Newsmax%20had%20picked%20up%20viewers%2C%20its%20total%20audience%20was%20still%20minuscule%20compared%20to%20Fox's%2C%20and%20neither%20it%20nor%20OAN%20had%20anything%20like%20the%20resources%20needed%20to%20compete%20effectively%20with%20Fox.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20days%20after%20the%20election%2C%20on%20November%209%202020%2C%20Fox%20News%20executives%20nonetheless%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2023%2F02%2F17%2Ffox-news-dominion-lawsuit-texts-election-claims%2F%5C%22%3Ecommitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20network%20to%20push%20%E2%80%9Cnarratives%20that%20would%20entice%20their%20audience%20back%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20double-talk%20of%20Fox%20News%20management%2C%20they%20resolved%20to%20%E2%80%9Crespect%E2%80%9D%20their%20audience%2C%20by%20which%20they%20meant%20reinforce%20their%20delusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20resulted%20in%20a%20mammoth%20turnaround.%20Within%20two%20weeks%2C%20Fox%20News%20had%20questioned%20the%20election%20result%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediamatters.org%2Ffox-news%2Ffox-news-has-cast-doubt-or-pushed-conspiracy-theories-about-election-results-nearly-600%5C%22%3E774%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Media%20Matters%20for%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20this%20switch%20of%20strategy%20meant%20the%20network%20was%20deliberately%20promoting%20a%20falsehood%20seems%20not%20to%20have%20troubled%20any%20of%20them.%20Nor%20did%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%2C%20in%20the%20words%20of%20their%20sister%20publication%2C%20the%20Post%2C%20undermining%20faith%20in%20democracy%20and%20the%20nation.%20The%20key%20thing%20was%20that%20the%20audiences%20came%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20truth%20comes%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20focused%20on%20promoting%20claims%20of%20electoral%20fraud%2C%20the%20network's%20primary%20targets%20soon%20included%20the%20two%20companies%20that%20provided%20electronic%20voting%20equipment%20for%20the%20election%20%E2%80%93%20Dominion%20Voting%20Systems%20and%20Smartmatic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20political%20battleground%2C%20there%20were%20rarely%20tangible%20consequences%20for%20running%20baseless%20stories.%20But%20Fox%20had%20wandered%20into%20a%20legal%20minefield.%20And%20it%20was%20not%20tiptoeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20lawyer%2C%20Sidney%20Powell%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fmedia%2F2020%2F12%2F01%2Fsidney-powell-trump-fox%2F%5C%22%3Ealleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20companies%20that%20had%20administered%20the%20voting%20machines%20had%20committed%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20massive%20and%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20egregious%20fraud%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20seen%E2%80%9D.%20Lou%20Dobbs%20was%20perhaps%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fmedia%2F3941539-settlement-reached-in-defamation-lawsuit-against-lou-dobbs-fox-news%2F%5C%22%3Eoutspoken%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Fox%20News%20presenters%2C%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Can%20electoral%209%2F11%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccyber%20Pearl%20Harbour%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDominion%20sent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fint.nyt.com%2Fdata%2Fdocumenttools%2Fredacted-documents-in-dominion-fox-news-case%2Fdca5e3880422426f%2Ffull.pdf%5C%22%3E3%2C600%20communications%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Fox%20News%20denying%20the%20various%20accusations%20to%20no%20effect.%20Then%20it%20mounted%20a%20defamation%20legal%20action.%20The%20case%20went%20on%20for%20several%20months%2C%20and%20on%20the%20day%20the%20trial%20was%20about%20to%20begin%2C%20Fox%20settled.%20The%20result%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ffox-news-dominion-lawsuit-trial-trump-2020-0ac71f75acfacc52ea80b3e747fb0afe%5C%22%3Emassive%20defamation%20payout%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20US%24787.5%20million%20(A%241.2%20billion).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20not%20only%20the%20expense%2C%20it%20was%20the%20embarrassment.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20discovery%20process%20and%20the%20depositions%20required%2C%20Dominion%20gained%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ftucker-carlson-fox-news-dominion-lawsuit-trump-5d6aed4bc7eb1f7a01702ebea86f37a1%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20internal%20Fox%20News%20documents%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20stark%20contrast%20between%20what%20the%20network's%20personalities%20said%20in%20private%20and%20what%20went%20to%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurdoch%2C%20in%20his%20deposition%2C%20said%20he%20never%20believed%20any%20of%20the%20claims%20of%20computer%20fraud.%20The%20internal%20communications%20also%20showed%20how%20deeply%20he%20detested%20Trump.%20After%20the%20January%206%202021%20riots%20at%20the%20US%20Capitol%2C%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20that%20he%20aimed%20to%20make%20Trump%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F2%2F28%2F23617987%2Ffox-news-rupert-murdoch-dominion-trump-election-fraud%5C%22%3Enon-person%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20response%20to%20these%20revelations%20was%20swift%20and%20predictable.%20On%20his%20Truth%20Social%20platform%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Ftrump-blames-rino-paul-ryan-fox-news-stance-rigged-election-1784915%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20honestly%20believes%20that%20the%20Presidential%20Election%20of%202020%2C%20despite%20MASSIVE%20amounts%20of%20proof%20to%20the%20contrary%2C%20was%20not%20Rigged%20and%20Stollen%20%5Bsic%5D%2C%20then%20he%20and%20his%20group%20of%20MAGA%20%5BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%5D%20Hating%20Globalist%20RINOS%20%5BRepublican%20in%20name%20only%5D%20should%20get%20out%20of%20the%20News%20Business%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20because%20they%20are%20aiding%20and%20abetting%20the%20DESTRUCTION%20OF%20AMERICA%20with%20FAKE%20NEWS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ETrump's%20resurrection%20and%20Murdoch's%20isolation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20schism%20between%20Trump%20and%20Murdoch%20was%20deep%20and%20bitter.%20Fox's%20subsequent%20search%20for%20an%20alternative%20to%20Trump%20was%20most%20publicly%20visible%20in%20late%202022%20and%20early%202023.%20In%20the%202022%20US%20midterm%20elections%2C%20the%20Democrats%20did%20much%20better%20than%20expected%2C%20and%20Trump-endorsed%20candidates%20performed%20poorly.%20The%20shining%20exception%20for%20Republicans%20was%20the%20governor%20of%20Florida%2C%20Ron%20DeSantis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurdoch%20embraced%20him.%20Always%20subtle%2C%20a%20New%20York%20Post%20front%20page%20anointed%20him%20%E2%80%9CDeFuture%E2%80%9D%20and%20later%20had%20a%20caricature%20of%20Trump%20as%20Humpty%20Dumpty%2C%20headlined%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2022%2F11%2F10%2Funder-fire-trump-against-blasts-press-the-enemy-of-the-people%2F%5C%22%3ETrumpty%20Dumpty%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeSantis%20was%20a%20determined%20cultural%20warrior%2C%20and%20no%20doubt%20Murdoch%20and%20others%20hoped%20he%20could%20represent%20%E2%80%9CTrumpism%E2%80%9D%20without%20the%20legal%20and%20personal%20baggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20DeSantis%20proved%20to%20be%20Trumpism%20without%20a%20hint%20of%20charisma.%20Nor%20did%20DeSantis%20dare%20question%20Trump's%20narrative%20of%20victimhood%2C%20endorsing%20his%20claims%20of%20a%20stolen%20election%20and%20that%20the%20legal%20cases%20against%20him%20were%20political%20witch%20hunts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20late%202023%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20DeSantis%20was%20going%20to%20lose%20the%20Republican%20primaries%20to%20be%20the%202024%20presidential%20nominee%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20Trump%20was%20going%20to%20win%20again.%20All%20business%20logic%20pointed%20towards%20the%20need%20for%20Fox%20News%20to%20make%20amends%20with%20Trump.%20And%20for%20Trump%2C%20political%20logic%20pointed%20towards%20the%20need%20for%20a%20d%C3%A9tente%20with%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20influential%20conservative%20media%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rapprochement%20began%20in%20January%202024.%20Fox%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ffox-trump-2024-election-e0b49cf505a0cc8f8779b6d7e4cadef0%5C%22%3Estaged%20a%20town%20hall%20event%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Trump%2C%20the%20first%20time%20he%20had%20been%20live%20on%20the%20network%20for%20two%20years.%20It%20not%20only%20gave%20Trump%20a%20platform%2C%20but%20it%20was%20timed%20to%20overshadow%20the%20other%20Republican%20presidential%20candidates%20having%20a%20debate%20on%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fbrianstelter%2Fstatus%2F1745881997736575047%23%5C%22%3EDeSantis%20was%20angry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20Trump%20has%20%E2%80%9Cgot%20a%20Praetorian%20Guard%20of%20the%20conservative%20media%2C%20Fox%20News%2C%20the%20websites%2C%20all%20this%20stuff%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20final%20act%20of%20obeisance%2C%20Murdoch%20attended%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention.%20But%20it%20merely%20underlined%20his%20new%20marginality.%20Trump%2C%20himself%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNvZv8BpJnu4%5C%22%3Ewas%20polite%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20speak%20with%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20a%20lot.%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20He's%20100%25%20sharp%2C%20he's%20sharp%20as%20a%20tack.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20Jr%2C%20now%20the%20self-proclaimed%20MAGA%20enforcer%2C%20was%20less%20polite.%20He%20claimed%20he%20had%20been%20blacklisted%20by%20Fox%20News%2C%20which%20Fox%20denied.%20Then%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMayneReport%2Fstatus%2F1813505074523697559%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethere%20was%20a%20time%20where%20if%20your%20wanted%20to%20survive%20in%20the%20Republican%20Party%20you%20had%20to%20bend%20the%20knee%20to%20%5BMurdoch%5D%20or%20to%20others.%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20the%20case%20any%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20annoy%20Murdoch%20further%2C%20one%20of%20the%20stars%20of%20the%20convention%20was%20Tucker%20Carlson%2C%20who%20was%20fired%20by%20Fox%2015%20months%20earlier.%20Carlson%20sat%20in%20Trump's%20VIP%20box%20next%20to%20the%20ex-president%2C%20while%20Murdoch%20was%20some%20distance%20away%20in%20a%20separate%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Murdoch%20seemed%20to%20have%20zero%20influence%20over%20Trump's%20vice%20presidential%20choice%2C%20and%20perhaps%20was%20even%20counterproductive.%20There%20were%20reports%20he%20had%20lobbied%20against%20the%20selection%20of%20JD%20Vance%2C%20while%20Donald%20Trump%20Jr%20and%20Carlson%20were%20both%20extremely%20proactive%20in%20pushing%20Vance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlson%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F07%2F16%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-vance-vp-decision.html%3Faction%3Dclick%26module%3DRelatedLinks%26pgtype%3DArticle%5C%22%3Eadvised%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20your%20enemies%20are%20pushing%20a%20running%20mate%20at%20you%E2%80%9D%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Murdoch%20empire%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit's%20a%20pretty%20good%20sign%20you%20should%20ignore%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20damage%20has%20been%20done%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20serves%20to%20underline%20Trump's%20continued%20dominance.%20To%20advance%20in%20the%20Republican%20Party%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20pay%20homage%20to%20Trump%20and%20his%20fictions.%20Ahead%20of%20the%202022%20midterm%20elections%2C%20The%20Washington%20Post%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2Frepublican-trump-2022-midterms-election-falsehoods%2F2021%2F07%2F04%2F3a43438c-d36f-11eb-ae54-515e2f63d37d_story.html%5C%22%3Elooked%20at%3C%2Fa%3E%20nearly%20700%20Republican%20candidates%20for%20federal%20office%20and%20found%20that%20at%20least%20a%20third%20embraced%20Trump's%20false%20election%20fraud%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20the%20party%20subjected%20to%20his%20worldview%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20new%20group%20of%20influential%2C%20pro-Trump%2C%20mega-donor%20billionaires%2C%20whose%20influence%20may%20be%20increasing%2C%20and%20whose%20views%20could%2C%20at%20best%2C%20be%20called%20eccentric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20for%20example%2C%20seemed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Felections%2Felon-musk-has-said-he-is-committing-around-45-million-a-month-to-a-new-pro-trump-super-pac-dda53823%5C%22%3Epromise%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20would%20give%20a%20pro-Trump%20political%20action%20committee%20US%2445%20million%20(A%2468%20million)%20a%20month%2C%20but%20in%20true%20Trumpian%20fashion%2C%20later%20seemed%20to%20backtrack.%20Musk%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Ftech%2F2024%2F07%2F22%2Felon-musk-jordan-peterson-interview%2F74506785007%2F%5C%22%3Ebelieves%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20woke%20mind%20virus%E2%80%9D%20is%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20greatest%20threats%20to%20modern%20civilisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20tech%20billionaire%2C%20Peter%20Thiel%2C%20Vance's%20principal%20backer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cato-unbound.org%2F2009%2F04%2F13%2Fpeter-thiel%2Feducation-libertarian%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20no%20lon