end.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20his%20social%20life%20disappear%20and%20his%20situation%20worsen%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Nirbhik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20training%20under%20his%20physiotherapist%20for%208-10%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20Prateek%20carefully%20monitored%20how%20his%20bladder%20and%20stomach%20reacted%20to%20every%20bite%20of%20food%20and%20sip%20of%20liquid.%20%E2%80%9CRecovery%20involved%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20improvement%20comes%20slowly%2C%20but%20persistence%20is%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202017%2C%20he%20could%20stand%20with%20a%20walker%20and%20perform%20tasks%20like%20cooking%2C%20and%20even%20use%20crutches.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20he%20wondered%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20I%20stop%20living%20my%20life%20when%20my%20mind%20and%20spirit%20are%20free%20despite%20my%20challenges%3F%20I%20am%20ambitious%2C%20a%20big-time%20foodie%2C%20and%20love%20meeting%20my%20friends.%20Why%20should%20a%20wheelchair%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20not%20to%20let%20his%20wheelchair%20limit%20him%2C%20he%20began%20reaching%20out%20to%20his%20friends%20after%20four%20years%20of%20isolation.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20they%20were%20initially%20unsure%2C%20they%20eventually%20realised%20I%20was%20still%20the%20same%20person%20and%20invited%20me%20back%20into%20their%20social%20circles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20family%20struggled%20to%20find%20accessible%20locations%20for%20Prateek%2C%20so%20they%20took%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20install%20ramps.%20This%20way%2C%20he%20could%20join%20them%20in%20their%20outings%20to%20restaurants%20and%20theatres.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20to%20start%20a%20big%20business%20but%20to%20improve%20accessibility%20for%20people%20like%20Prateek%2C%20helping%20them%20enjoy%20a%20life%20similar%20to%20anyone%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nirbhik%2C%20adding%20that%20being%20able%20to%20go%20out%20for%20weekends%20and%20date%20nights%20boosted%20Prateek%E2%80%99s%20confidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiving%20him%20a%20normal%20life%20was%20the%20biggest%20success%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20effort%20to%20reconnect%20with%20the%20community%2C%20Prateek%20faced%20a%20harsh%20reality%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360927%2Fsweta-mantrii-comedian-spina-bifida-disability-stand-up-comedy-wheelchair-accessibility-inclusion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lack%20of%20accessibility%20in%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Despite%20living%20in%20a%20prestigious%20building%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20neither%20the%20building%20itself%20nor%20public%20spaces%20like%20banks%2C%20restaurants%2C%20metro%20or%20police%20stations%2C%20theatres%20were%20accessible%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20realisation%20hit%20me%20hard%2C%20making%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20were%20in%20a%20permanent%20lockdown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20with%20disabilities%20are%20forced%20to%20stay%20indoors%20because%20of%20such%20infrastructural%20barriers.%20The%20World%20Bank%20reports%20that%20about%2015%25%20of%20the%20global%20population%20has%20some%20form%20of%20disability.%20Given%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20of%20over%201.4%20billion%2C%20this%20translates%20to%20approximately%2021%20crore%20people%20with%20disabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20the%20question%3A%20Where%20are%20these%20individuals%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disabled%20community%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20often%20unseen%20and%20confined%20to%20their%20homes.%20An%20important%20question%20to%20consider%20then%20is%20what%20the%20government%20is%20doing%20about%20accessibility.%20The%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(RPwD)%20Act%20of%202016%20mandates%20equal%20access%20and%20universal%20design%20standards%2C%20but%20enforcement%20is%20often%20inadequate%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20projects%20often%20feature%20substandard%20accessibility%20features%2C%20with%20ramps%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20meet%20necessary%20standards.%20There%20is%20a%20notable%20lack%20of%20action%20from%20startups%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20wheelchair%20advocates%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20remarks.%20To%20fill%20this%20gap%2C%20he%20created%20RampMyCity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRampMyCity%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20created%20just%20from%20my%20ideas%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20grew%20out%20of%20my%20real-life%20experiences.%20We%20visit%20each%20location%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20ramp%20requirements%20and%20then%20devise%20a%20solution%20that%20works%20without%20disrupting%20the%20current%20setup.%20Our%20approach%20is%20always%20practical%20and%20starts%20from%20the%20bottom%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20at%20RampMyCity%20visits%20each%20location%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20ramp%20requirements%20and%20then%20devise%20a%20solution%20that%20works%20without%20disrupting%20the%20current%20setup.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20at%20RampMyCity%20visits%20each%20location%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20ramp%20requirements%20and%20then%20devise%20a%20solution%20that%20works%20without%20disrupting%20the%20current%20setup.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20began%20with%20a%20campaign%20to%20persuade%20restaurants%20to%20install%20ramps%2C%20aiming%20to%20change%20the%20view%20of%20accessibility%20from%20a%20charity%20issue%20to%20a%20popular%20cause.%20Its%20first%20product%20was%20a%20simple%2C%20attention-grabbing%20ramp%20designed%20to%20make%20accessibility%20more%20visible%20and%20mainstream%20and%20promote%20it%20in%20popular%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20challenge%20for%20Prateek%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20awareness%20about%20the%20need%20for%20ramps%2C%20making%20it%20tough%20to%20attract%20sponsors.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20convincing%20is%20crucial%20when%20the%20need%20isn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20to%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRamps%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20any%20cement%20or%20brickwork.%20We%20decided%20to%20manufacture%20steel%20and%20aluminium%20ramps%20in%20our%20workshop%2C%20which%20can%20be%20quickly%20installed%20at%20any%20location%20with%20no%20downtime%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20This%20makes%20it%20a%20simple%20and%20efficient%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20RampMyCity%20focused%20on%20eateries%20because%20they%20attract%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%20Between%202018%20and%202020%2C%20it%20had%20set%20up%20ramps%20at%2060%20locations.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20our%20work%20became%20more%20visible%2C%20we%20began%20receiving%20requests%20from%20other%20sectors%20like%20banks%2C%20schools%