and%20mental%20challenges%2C%20my%20coach%20was%20very%20supportive.%20My%20mother%20too%20urged%20me%20to%20follow%20my%20dreams%2C%20as%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20follow%20hers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20gradually%20progressed%20from%20swimming%20for%20just%2020%20minutes%20to%20swimming%20for%20seven%20to%20eight%20hours%20in%20the%20pool.%20Later%2C%20she%20began%20practising%20in%20open%20water%2C%20training%20in%20the%20dams%20around%20Nashik%20over%20the%20weekends.%20Although%20she%20was%20slowly%20overcoming%20her%20physical%20challenges%2C%20she%20struggled%20to%20achieve%20the%20necessary%20speed%20for%20a%20100-metre%20lap%20during%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20was%20holding%20her%20back%20%E2%80%94%20her%20father%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20given%20her%20his%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKiran%20Chavan%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20his%20daughter%20wanted%20to%20put%20herself%20through%20such%20a%20demanding%20ordeal.%20He%20was%20apprehensive%2C%20knowing%20of%20people%20who%20had%20lost%20their%20lives%20attempting%20this%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20her%20to%20put%20herself%20in%20a%20life-threatening%20position.%20She%20was%20doing%20well%20in%20her%20business%2C%20as%20a%20mother%20and%20wife.%20Why%20put%20your%20life%20at%20risk%3F%20I%20wanted%20to%20protect%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kiran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tanvi%20was%20determined%20and%20persuasive.%20When%20letters%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20she%20asked%20her%20coach%20to%20convince%20her%20father.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20her%20coach%20met%20me%20and%20assured%20me%20that%20there%20was%20no%20risk%20of%20life%20and%20she%20would%20be%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20it%20convinced%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMagically%2C%20Tanvi%20was%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20required%20timing%20the%20next%20day%20and%20since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20She%20slowly%20gained%20her%20c