fellow%20swimmers%20were%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20attempts%20due%20to%20the%20worsening%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20waves%20were%20two%20to%20three%20metres%20in%20height%20and%20pulled%20you%20back%20to%20England.%20I%20was%20trapped%20in%20this%20and%20had%20to%20swim%20an%20extra%2010%20kilometres%20to%20reach%20the%20French%20coast%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Tanvi%20pressed%20on%20and%20covered%20the%20additional%2010%20kilometres%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20weather.%20When%20the%20observer%20asked%20if%20she%20wished%20to%20continue%2C%20it%20was%20an%20emphatic%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20actually%20wanted%20to%20give%20up.%20I%20had%20vomited%20and%20had%20zero%20energy.%20It%20was%20thanks%20to%20my%20coach%E2%80%99s%20training%20that%20I%20was%20mentally%20fit%20to%20continue.%20He%20had%20told%20me%20that%20it%20is%20on%20days%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20training%20are%20the%20days%20that%20you%20must%20show%20up.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20when%20your%20hands%20and%20legs%20reach%20their%20breaking%20point%2C%20you%20will%20feel%20like%20giving%20up.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20up!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20her%20morale%2C%20her%20husband%20showed%20her%20a%20video%20of%20their%20children%20and%20the%20coach%20showed%20her%20the%20Indian%20flag.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20swim%20for%20my%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%