ecycled%20plastic%20products%2C%20such%20as%20park%20benches%2C%20dustbins%2C%20planters%2C%20and%20other%20eco-friendly%20gift%20items.%20Employing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvalue-based%20recycling%20technology%E2%80%9D%20to%20manufacture%20them%2C%20%3Cem%3Eeconscious%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20sought%20to%20walk%20the%20talk%20on%20creating%20a%20circular%20economy%20around%20plastic%20waste%20and%20driving%20greater%20awareness%20for%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20business%20during%20COVID-19%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20early%20months%20of%20%3Cem%3Eeconscious%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewere%20both%20challenging%20and%20exciting.%20With%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20still%20affecting%20daily%20life%2C%20we%20had%20to%20navigate%20restrictions%20while%20developing%20our%20initial%20products.%20We%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20researching%20and%20prototyping%2C%20trying%20to%20find%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289275%2Fhyderabad-startup-banyan-nation-recycles-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-product-bottles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycle%20plastic%20waste%20into%20useful%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20project%20involved%20creating%20an%20eco-board%20out%20of%20plastic%20waste.%20This%20board%20was%20a%20prototype%20and%20could%20be%20used%20for%20multiple%20applications.%20This%20project%20was%20significant%20as%20it%20allowed%20us%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20our%20recycling%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20worked%20on%20creating%20eco-friendly%20gifting%20items%2C%20such%20as%20planters%20and%20coasters%2C%20which%20helped%20them%20reach%20a%20wider%20audience%20and%20spread%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20recycling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20much%20experimentation%2C%20we%20found%20that%20products%20that%20can%20be%20used%20in%20public%20spaces%20like%20benches%20and%20dustbins%20are%20suitable%20applications%20as%20they%20create%20awareness%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20about%20addressing%20plastic%20waste%20while%20also%20requiring%20vast%20amounts%20of%20recycled%20plastic.%20To%20make%20a%20bench%2C%20for%20example%2C%20we%20require%20approximately%2050%20kg%20of%20plastic%20waste.%20This%20way%20we%20could%20create%20a%20larger%20impact%20and%20soon%20we%20started%20developing%20such%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sonal%20was%20selected%20as%20a%20leader%20for%20the%20Women%20Climate%20Collective%202024%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20supporting%20emerging%20women%20leaders%20to%20lead%20climate%20action.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361509%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESonal%20was%20selected%20as%20a%20leader%20for%20the%20Women%20Climate%20Collective%202024%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20supporting%20emerging%20women%20leaders%20to%20lead%20climate%20action.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20to%20say%2C%20there%20were%20some%20real%20challenges%20they%20encountered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20started%20amid%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%20to%20source%20material%2C%20develop%20prototypes%20and%20obtain%20customer%20feedback.%20But%20we%20were%20able%20to%20connect%20with%20NGOs%2C%20corporate%20foundations%2C%20and%20local%20government%20authorities%20who%20shared%20our%20vision%20and%20supported%20our%20projects.%20Our%20partnerships%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20expanding%20our%20reach%20and%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInnovation%20has%20also%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20our%20journey.%20For%20example%2C%20our%20project%20to%20create%20park%20benches%20from%20recycled%20plastic%20required%20us%20to%20develop%20new%20methods%20and%20designs%20for%20processing%20and%20moulding%20the%20plastic%20waste.%20It%20showed%20us%20that%20being%20open%20to%20new%20ideas%20and%20continuously%20improving%20our%20processes%20can%20lead%20to%20successful%20outcomes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Delhi-based%20startup%2C%20the%20process%20begins%20with%20gathering%20plastic%20waste%20from%20various%20sources%2C%20including%20informal%20waste%20workers%20who%20collect%20materials%20from%20different%20locations.%20They%20also%20collaborate%20with%20NGOs%2C%20housing%20societies%2C%20and%20colleges%20to%20run%20awareness%20campaigns%20and%20collect%20plastic%20through%20source%20segregation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20collecting%20the%20plastic%20waste%2C%20we%20sort%20and%20clean%20it%20thoroughly.%20After%20the%20plastic%20waste%20is%20collected%2C%20it%20is%20meticulously%20sorted%20to%20separate%20different%20types%20of%20plastic.%20This%20sorting%20process%20is%20crucial%20because%20different%20plastics%20have%20different%20properties%20and%20melting%20points%2C%20which%20affect%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20final%20product%20as%20well%20as%20the%20recyclability%20of%20the%20recycled%20products.%20Hence%20we%20do%20not%20mix%20different%20plastic%20types%20ensuring%20it%20is%20again%20recyclable%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sonal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20%E2%80%98value-based%20recycling%20technology%E2%80%99%20that%20makes%20%3Cem%3Eeconscious%20%3C%2Fem%3Eunique%20and%20impactful%2C%20argues%20Sonal.%20Unlike%20traditional%20recycling%20methods%2C%20which%20often%20produce%20low-quality%20items%2C%20she%20claims%20their%20approach%20ensures%20that%20the%20recycled%20plastic%20products%20they%20create%20are%20high-quality%20and%20practical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTraditional%20recycling%20often%20involves%20turning%20plastic%20into%20small%20pellets%2C%20which%20consumes%20a%20lot%20of%20energy.%20Instead%2C%20we%20skip%20the%20pellet-making%20process%20and%20use%20plastic%20flakes.%20This%20choice%20not%20only%20saves%20energy%20but%20also%20reduces%20our%20environmental%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sonal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20turn%20these%20plastic%20flakes%20into%20eco-boards.%20This%20is%20where%20our%20value-based%20recycling%20plays%20a%20key%20role.%20The%20eco-boards%20are%20durable%20and%20versatile%2C%20serving%20as%20raw%20materials%20for%20various%20high-quality%20products%20and%20applications.%20This%20process%20is%20energy-efficient%20and%20helps%20maintain%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20plastic%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20create%20long-lasting%20and%20valuable%20items%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-1-1723642660.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20