20can%20be%20easily%20fabricated%20using%20regular%20cutting%20and%20woodworking%20methods%2C%20and%20for%20more%20intricate%20designs%2C%20CNC%20(computer%20numerical%20control)%20cutting%20can%20be%20applied%2C%20allowing%20for%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20precision%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sonal.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20this%20ability%20to%20customise%20the%20pattern%20and%20design%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20board%E2%80%99s%20durability%2C%20makes%20eco-boards%20a%20versatile%20material.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20suitable%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20applications%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20creating%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20products%20or%20functional%20items%20with%20a%20longer%20lifespan.%20The%20process%20up-cycles%20plastic%20waste%20and%20also%20adds%20value%20by%20transforming%20it%20into%20high-quality%2C%20visually%20appealing%2C%20and%20sustainable%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20eco-boards%20are%20then%20used%20to%20make%20a%20range%20of%20products%2C%20including%20park%20benches%2C%20dustbins%2C%20planters%2C%20and%20other%20eco-friendly%20gift%20items.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-03-1723642502.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%E2%80%99s%20their%20'value-based%20recycling%20(plastic)%20technology'%20that%20makes%20econscious%20unique%20and%20impactful.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-03-1723642502.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-03-1723642502-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-03-1723642502-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0