20and%20which%20didn%E2%80%99t.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20times%20when%20people%20seemed%20to%20feel%20awkward%20to%20watch%20a%20disabled%20person%20go%20on%20the%20stage%20and%20get%20uncomfortable%20to%20laugh%20at%20their%20jokes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20Sweta%20acknowledges%20that%20her%20jokes%20might%20have%20been%20a%20bit%20harsh%20as%20she%20was%20still%20learning%20the%20subtleties%20of%20comedy%20and%20effective%20delivery.%20Now%2C%20she%20spends%20the%20first%20few%20minutes%20easing%20the%20audience%20into%20her%20performance%20before%20delivering%20her%20strongest%20jokes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fstrong%3EWill%20I%20even%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20stage%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20comedian%20is%20offered%20a%20gig%2C%20they%20usually%20ask%3A%20How%20many%20minutes%20will%20I%20be%20performing%20for%3F%20How%20much%20does%20it%20pay%3F%20Sweta%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20are%20focused%20more%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312600%2Fhow-can-india-be-more-disabled-friendly-inclusive-planning-in-public-events%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20issue%20of%20accessibility%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CIs%20the%20venue%20accessible%20for%20me%3F%20Is%20there%20an%20accessible%20restroom%20available%3F%20How%20many%20steps%20are%20there%2C%20and%20how%20long%20will%20it%20take%20to%20get%20to%20the%20stage%3F%20Will%20I%20even%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20stage%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20of%20her%20early%20comedy%20shows%2C%20she%20faced%20a%20tough%20setup%20with%20a%20mat%20that%20was%20slippery%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20her%20to%20manage%20her%20crutch.%20When%20the%20audience%20saw%20her%20struggle%2C%20it%20created%20tension%20in%20the%20room.%20She%20recalls%20that%20while%20previous%20comics%20had%20successfully%20warmed%20up%2